modules.description: Converts time zone values to and from JSON format using Yojson, enabling serialization and deserialization. Parses time zone identifiers from strings into structured time zone values. Useful for handling time zone data in JSON-based APIs or configuration files.

Converts time zone values to and from JSON using Yojson, supporting serialization and deserialization of time zone identifiers. Parses time zone strings into structured values for use in JSON-based APIs or configuration files.
